PROJECT-3 MusicPlayer

A basic Music Player built using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript â€” all in one file! This player supports Play, Pause, and Stop functions with a clean, minimal UI.

Features:

Play / Pause / Stop controls Simple and responsive layout Supports both online and local audio files No external libraries needed

Tech Stack:

HTML CSS JavaScript

How to Use: Clone or download the repository. Open index.html in your browser. Replace the src in the tag with your audio file (or online URL). Click play and enjoy the music!
